# Apple macOS Design Language — Miragenty

Build interfaces that feel like they belong on the user's Mac. Every pixel should say "Apple built this."

## Core Philosophy

- **Clarity**: Content is king. UI is a container, not a destination. Minimize chrome.
- **Deference**: Interface elements step back so content shines through. Use translucency and blur to imply depth without competing for attention.
- **Depth**: Layered surfaces with blur, shadows, and vibrancy create a physical sense of space.

**Font policy**: Apple style REQUIRES system fonts — do NOT use custom display fonts or Google Fonts for UI text. SF Mono is acceptable for code blocks.

---

## Layout

Three-panel structure (Top Bar + Sidebar + Content). 8px base grid.

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  ● ● ●  │         Top Bar (48-52px)             │  ← draggable
├──────────┼──────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Sidebar  │                                      │
│ 220-260px│         Main Content                 │
│ vibrancy │         (solid background)           │
│          │                                      │
├──────────┴──────────────────────────────────────┤
│              Bottom Bar (optional)               │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

- Top bar: 48-52px, doubles as window drag zone. Sparse — search, view toggles, global actions only.
- Sidebar: 220-260px, translucent with vibrancy. Sections with small-caps headers. Active item = subtle highlight, not loud color.
- Content: solid/opaque background for readability. This is the star — minimize surrounding chrome.
- Traffic lights: top-left, integrated into sidebar or top bar. 12px circles, 8px spacing. Red #FF5F57, Yellow #FEBC2E, Green #28C840. Gray #CDCDCD when inactive.

---

## Typography

```css
/* UI text — MUST use system fonts */
font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "SF Pro Display", "SF Pro Text",
             "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;

/* Code / monospace */
font-family: "SF Mono", "Menlo", "Monaco", "Courier New", monospace;
```

| Role        | Size | Weight   | Line Height |
|-------------|------|----------|-------------|
| Large Title | 26px | Bold 700 | 32px        |
| Title 1     | 22px | Regular  | 28px        |
| Title 2     | 17px | Regular  | 22px        |
| Title 3     | 15px | Semi 600 | 20px        |
| Body        | 13px | Regular  | 18px        |
| Callout     | 12px | Regular  | 16px        |
| Caption     | 11px | Regular  | 14px        |
| Mini        | 9px  | Medium   | 12px        |

Letter-spacing: -0.01em to -0.03em for headlines. Use opacity or secondary color for de-emphasis, not lighter weight.

