## Corner Radii

| Element        | Radius |
|----------------|--------|
| Window         | 10px   |
| Modal / Panel  | 12px   |
| Card           | 8px    |
| Button         | 6px    |
| Input          | 6px    |
| Tag / Badge    | 4px    |
| Toggle (pill)  | 14px   |
| Tooltip        | 4px    |

Nested rounded corners: parent radius = content padding + child radius.

