## Blur, Vibrancy & Translucency

```css
.sidebar, .toolbar, .floating-panel {
  backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(20px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(20px);
}

/* Light sidebar */
.sidebar { background: rgba(246, 246, 246, 0.72); }

/* Dark sidebar */
@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
  .sidebar { background: rgba(30, 30, 30, 0.72); }
}
```

Use blur on: sidebars, top bars, floating panels, popovers, toasts, command palette.
Do NOT blur: main content area, modal overlays (use semi-transparent dark overlay), body text containers.
Always include `saturate(180%)` to prevent washed-out colors.

